  <brief_title>CICATRIX in the Treatment of Recent Post-surgical Scars</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of CICATRIX (Asian Gotu Kola or Pennywort) in the Treatment of Recent Post-surgical Scars</official_title>
  <sponsors>
